  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of Site Facilitation, Reception Management, Emergency Shelter and Non-Food Items(NFI) Assistance in North-East Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Since the inception of the counter insurgency operations in 2017, the trend of new arrivals from hard-to-reach areas to accessible locations across Borno State has increased significantly and at an alarming rate. In response to the needs identified and the strategy defined by the camp coordination and camp management, shelter and non-food items (NFI) sectors, IOM supports the continuation and scaling-up of assistance within the areas of site facilitation, reception management, emergency shelter and NFIs.</narrative>
  </description>
